title: The Story of Washed Up Emo
itunes:title: The Story of Washed Up Emo
description:
Episode 175 - The podcast world collides with this split episode on The Story of Washed Up Emo and my friend Tom Mullen. In this show, we talk about why we do both our shows, how to keep engaged in music and the TRUE meaning of screamo. It was a fun experiment and I hope you enjoy the conversation held within. Try the amazing pop/geek culture mailing service, Loot Crate for all your collectable needs. Sign up now and get $3 your new subscription.Pre-order the new H2O record "Use Your Voice" from our friends at Bridge Nine Records. Their first in 7 years!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
